txt.en: 'You have done me a great service bringing yourselves here.'
'Have you finally realized that none can withstand the Dark Lord?'
'No matter, my champions will make quick work of you.'
'Or maybe the Free Peoples have gathered the courage to stand against all of my champions at once?'
'Surely brave  warriors such as yourselves do not fear a fair fight?'
